**  MSG
E-01 INPUT PART NO. OR ISSUED DATE
E-02 INCORRECT DATE.
E-03 NO DATA FOR INQUIRY.
E-04 NO FOLLOWING DATA.
E-05 NO PREVIOUS DATA.
E-06 INCORRECT NO.
E-07 FOR REVERSED DELIVERY TIME,CANNOT ENTER NONEXISTENT PROCESS.
E-08 INCORRECT OPTION.
E-09 INCORRECT PLAN DATE.
E-10 REVERSED DELIVERY DATE LATER THAN LATER PROCESS.
E-11 UPDATE (CMD-5) ONLY BY PRODUCTION CONTROL SECTION STAFF.
E-12 N/C BOX QUANTITY IS NOT ENTERED.
E-13 STOP DATE IS INCORRECT.
E-14 STOP DATE IS NOT ENTERED.
E-15 DEPARTMENT OF DEFECT OCCURRENCE NOT ENTERED.
E-16 ONLY DELETE CODE '0' IS VALID.
E-17 THE DATA HAS ALREADY BEEN DELETED.
E-18 NO DATA FOR 8TH PROCESS OR HIGHER.
E-19 THIS IS THE TOP PROCESS SCREEN.
E-20 THIS IS THE BOTTOM PROCESS SCREEN.
E-21 INPUT '*' FOR NO COVER
